[package]
name = "wayland-backend"
version = "0.3.4"
authors = [ "Elinor Berger <elinor@safaradeg.net>",]
edition = "2021"
rust-version = "1.65"
repository = "https://github.com/smithay/wayland-rs"
documentation = "https://docs.rs/wayland-backend/"
license = "MIT"
categories = [ "gui", "api-bindings",]
keywords = [ "wayland",]
description = "Low-level bindings to the Wayland protocol"
readme = "README.md"
build = "build.rs"

[dependencies]
scoped-tls = "1.0"
downcast-rs = "1.2"

[build-dependencies]
cc = "1.0"

[dev-dependencies]
concat-idents = "1.1"
env_logger = "0.10"

[features]
client_system = [ "wayland-sys/client",]
server_system = [ "wayland-sys/server",]
dlopen = [ "wayland-sys/dlopen",]

[dependencies.wayland-sys]
version = "0.31.2"
path = "../wayland-sys"
features = []

[dependencies.log]
version = "0.4"
optional = true

[dependencies.raw-window-handle]
version = "0.5.0"
optional = true

[dependencies.rwh_06]
package = "raw-window-handle"
version = "0.6.0"
optional = true

[dependencies.smallvec]
version = "1.9"
features = [ "union", "const_generics", "const_new",]

[dependencies.rustix]
version = "0.38.17"
features = [ "event", "fs", "net", "process",]

[dev-dependencies.wayland-scanner]
path = "../wayland-scanner"

[dev-dependencies.wayland-sys]
path = "../wayland-sys"
features = [ "client", "server",]

[package.metadata.docs.rs]
all-features = true
rustdoc-args = [ "--cfg", "docsrs",]

[package]
name = "wayland-sys"
version = "0.31.2"
repository = "https://github.com/smithay/wayland-rs"
documentation = "https://docs.rs/wayland-sys/"
authors = [ "Elinor Berger <elinor@safaradeg.net>",]
description = "FFI bindings to the various libwayland-*.so libraries. You should only need this crate if you are working on custom wayland protocol extensions. Look at the crate wayland-client for usable bindings."
license = "MIT"
categories = [ "external-ffi-bindings",]
edition = "2021"
rust-version = "1.65"
readme = "README.md"

[dependencies]
log = "0.4"

[build-dependencies]
pkg-config = "0.3.7"

[features]
dlopen = [ "once_cell",]
client = []
cursor = [ "client",]
egl = [ "client",]
server = [ "libc", "memoffset",]

[dependencies.dlib]
version = "0.5.1"

[dependencies.libc]
version = "0.2"
optional = true

[dependencies.once_cell]
version = "1.0"
optional = true

[dependencies.memoffset]
version = "0.9"
optional = true

[package.metadata.docs.rs]
all-features = true
rustdoc-args = [ "--cfg", "docsrs",]
